A4.text: Kath Soucie has voiced Lola Bunny in multiple media including Space Jam (1996), New Looney Tunes (2015–2020), and Looney Tunes World of Mayhem (2018–present).

A5.text: Kath Soucie reprises her voice in both Tweety's High-Flying Adventure and Looney Tunes Racing.
